These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: gospel, metal, salsa, folk, country, jazz, r&b
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of gospel is on the left of the fan of folk##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of country is between the fan of gospel and the fan of salsa##2
5. the fan of folk is between the fan of metal and the fan of gospel##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b | salsa | country | gospel | folk | metal | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: reading, magic-tricks, woodworking, hiking, video-games, gardening, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is reading##2
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Hobby   | gardening | drawing | reading | woodworking | hiking | magic-tricks | video-games |

 #################################

 
