5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is photography##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Hobby   | drawing | camping | writing | photography | board-games | gardening | chess |

