2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | skydiving | board-games | card-games | gardening | video-games | baking |

