3. the owner of the guinea-pig is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the cat and the owner of the pony##2
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1  |     2      |  3  |  4   |    5     |   6   |  7   |
| Pet   | goldfish | ferret | mouse | guinea-pig | cat | turtle | pony |

